text: Dientje Meijer-Haantjes (17 March 1918 - 5 October 1994) was a Dutch gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Dutch female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
